      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.AccountController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.AccountController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Endpoints for user accounts: login/logout, registration, two-factor\nauthentication (TOTP), password reset and e-mail verification. Sessions are\nissued via an HttpOnly JWT cookie plus a CSRF double-submit cookie.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.ChatController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.ChatController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.ChatController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.ChatController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Read access to chat history. All endpoints require an authenticated user.\nReal-time delivery of new messages is handled by <xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.ChatHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>;\nthis controller only serves the persisted message history.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.EventsController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.EventsController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.EventsController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.EventsController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages calendar events, both personal (no workspace) and workspace-shared, including\ncreation, editing, deletion and various queries (counts, lists, linked workspace). All\nendpoints require an authenticated user. Changes to workspace events are pushed live to\nthe workspace group over the <xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.EventHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.FoldersController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.FoldersController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.FoldersController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.FoldersController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages note folders, both personal (no workspace) and workspace-shared, including\ncreation, editing, moving and recursive deletion. All endpoints require an\nauthenticated user. Changes to workspace folders are pushed live to the workspace\ngroup over the <xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.NoteHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.FriendshipController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.FriendshipController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.FriendshipController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.FriendshipController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages friendships: sending, accepting and rejecting friend requests, removing\nfriends, and listing incoming/outgoing requests and current friends. All endpoints\nrequire an authenticated user. Changes are pushed live to the affected user over the\n<xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.ChatHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> so clients update without a reload.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.NotesController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.NotesController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.NotesController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.NotesController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages notes and their content modules — text blocks and link items — both personal\n(no workspace) and workspace-shared. Covers creating, editing, moving, ordering and\ndeleting notes and modules, plus various queries. All endpoints require an authenticated\nuser. Changes to workspace notes are pushed live to the workspace group over the\n<xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.NoteHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.TodoListsController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.TodoListsController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.TodoListsController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.TodoListsController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages todo lists and their entries, both personal (no workspace) and workspace-shared,\nincluding creation, editing, deletion and various queries. All endpoints require an\nauthenticated user. Changes to workspace items are pushed live to the workspace group\nover the <xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.TodoHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.UsersController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.UsersController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.UsersController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.UsersController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">User profile and account management plus user discovery: editing the current user's\nprofile and avatar, deleting the account, reading profile/account/preview data by ID or\nfor the current user, recent activity (todos/events/notes), related users, and user\nsearch. All endpoints require an authenticated user.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.WorkspaceController.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/lumify.api.Controllers.WorkspaceController.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "lumify.api.Controllers.WorkspaceController",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/lumify.api.Controllers.WorkspaceController.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages workspaces (shared spaces) and their memberships: creating, renaming and\ndeleting workspaces, adding and removing members, and querying workspaces and members.\nAll endpoints require an authenticated user. Changes are pushed live to every affected\nmember over the <xref href=\"lumify.api.Hubs.WorkspaceHub\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
